data.description: This home is available for immediate Move in!!! Look no further! Now is your chance to own this massive house on a beautiful corner lot, conveniently located close to Ft. Cavazos. This craftsman home features a stunning foyer with a staircase that screams elegance the moment you walk in the front door. This home also boasts 4 large rooms a living/game room upstairs, 2.5 bathrooms and a large kitchen for your family, or just for entertaining. Just minutes from the school and within walking distance to the park, you will love this home whether it is your starter home or your forever home. Stop browsing homes this is the one you want!
